HEADWORD: Re-resolve
<hw>Re`-re*solve"</hw> <pr>(r?`r?-z?lv")</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos>
<def>To resolve again.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Resolves, and <qex>re-resolves</qex>, then dies the same.</q>
